reviews.review_text: Love coming to this place for interior decor. When the holidays come around it is the best place to get quality themed kitchen ware and decor. They have so many different options. From clothing to gym equipment to stationary. Find great things the more often you visit.
Always enjoy the occasional shopping trip to Winners. This is a spacious store with plenty of parking. Dog-Friendly, too!

Shout out to the home sense team! We bought a sofa here and from start to finish staff were friendly and very helpful. They help me load the sofa into my truck as well! Cant say enough good things about this location! Great job!
Great offers, nice pricing. Really worth visiting it.
Nisha and Eva very helpful and kind. We bought a Muvado wrist watch and a marble top side table if it helps to remember us! Thanks for the service!

Every thing you need around your house, your patio, is right here...8 acres under covered air conditioning big supercenter. There Are shoes.., jewellery, fashions too... My son found 2 exceptionally comfy, large cushions, for his big van..to rest at the back of van ...on long trips like driving up prince George. Price is good. A spacious stores. Lots of parking and customers, despite in a pretty remote location in Burnaby. I can see lots customers, Lots of choices for happy campers..moving bought products onto their vehicle.

The Winners & Homesence combination store is the only way to go if you plan on spending money. I cant imagine walking out of this combination store without something I needed. If you like something, but you dont like making impulsive shopping decisions, my suggestion is to go and have a coffee or take a little breather outside. Make the decision whether you ARE or NOT going to buy after you remove yourself from all the stimulation of all the stuff set up in such a way that you cant help but desire it ...but just make sure that you dont remove yourself for too long. Because if you go home and think about it and come to decide, after a good nights sleep, that you absolutely MUST have it...guess what its no longer going to be there. It will be GONE. This has happened to me so many times!! This is how I used to make purchases. Any item that I loved when I was in the store and was still thinking about the next day, would be something I believed worth buying. There is such a range of stylish on-trend clothes, accessories, make-up, furniture, decor etc from sandals & giant wall clocks to doggie dresses & mens cologne that you will find what you forgot you needed without much effort at all and at decent prices. Check out my pretty towels and the cutest ever portable doggy bed.
Always great items
Very spacious store with good variety of things. From clothes to beauty item you will surely find something to buy. Employees are helpful and store is well maintained :)
Awesome place to find things for home decor and fashion.

HomeSense really disappoints. The prices arent as good as they used to be, but whoever does the buying is a genius. Although the clothing is pretty nice and winners, I find that they dont always keep up to the newest fashion trends. However the buyer is for the jewelry department really picked some gorgeous pieces. Husbands and boyfriends listen up, this is a great place to get a beautiful piece of jewelry for your loved one at a pretty reasonable price.
This is hands down the best winners / home sense in Vancouver for selection and quality of product.

I am like a kid on a candy store when visiting Winners & HomeSense. Always grab a cart because even if you don t intend to purchase something I guarantee you, you will not walk out empty handed  . Love the selection they offer, always something new. Staff is always super nice, especially the ladies in the jewellery department. Big plus that they allow dogs and convenient parking is a huge bonus.

Winners 5771 Marine way, Burnaby is my favourite store. Not only is the store specious with lots of beautiful selection with good prices  but the workers are so nice as well especially Raj. She s very helpful all the time and is great with customers.
Good sized homesense and winners with lots of furniture options. Have received great carry out service twice when purchasing furniture
Large, clean, and easy to navigate aisles.
Love love love this location. Its well organized and clean with very friendly staff. Ill go out of my way to shop here.

Excellent customer service.  I was so very impressed with Manager Tracey with all she did for us with what we thought was lost but later found it (left it on the counter at the other store).   This was out first time going to this store but I think we will make this our go to store now.

Lots of wonderful little finds here and there. I scored big once, finding some really good white and black truffle oil. Delicious and so flagrant! They have all different types of snacks and dried pasta too. The home decor section always there for over an hour. This location also have a few furniture pieces and area rugs, big and small. The shoes are lacking a bit in terms of size 6 but then again when it is not anywhere else? Take a look around the pots and pans while youre at it, the masterclass brand that I found there is actually very durable and totally non stick.i basically use it for everything now. Staff is helpful when you can find one

My favorite Winners. Lots of home decor and larger furniture items. Good selection of clothes and shoes. Some toys too that are really high quality. They have a good return policy, no hassle, no attitude, no questions. All in all a positive shopping experience.
The staff is helpful, I have a good shopping experience at this location. Specially the cashier Sana.D is awesome that she was super patient and friendly:)

I love the clearance sections here. Theres always a bargain to be had. There three clearance sections. One is where you find the cosmetics, and bathroom beauty items, there are rows of clearance items here. Then you have the gourmet food section that has great discounts and then if you check out the home decor section you have more discounts on home decor items like candles, journals, etc. Theres always huge deals to be found.
a great store for shopping with great prices

Really Amazing Customer service. Special thanks to Yash for helping me out and having such a friendly behaviour.! I m glad to visit winners after such a boring day and because of him i had an amazing shopping experience. Adios! Hope to meet you again on my next visit.

I shop here quite frequently and today (July 22) was the first time I received outstanding customer service at the fitting room. His name is Bryan , he greeted me with a smile , he was friendly and pleasant to chat with. He s been on the job for about 2 months. I ve been in customer service since 1986, and have come to expect great customer service but unfortunately it s lacking nowadays. Those 5       are for Bryan!
